She has extensive experience leading teams in various registrarial roles, including admissions, assessment, convocation, fees and scheduling, financial aid, systems and reporting, and registration and audit. Janene started her career at George Brown in 2003 as an operations manager in the Registrar’s office. Janene has been recognized with several awards for her leadership, including the Sheridan Inspirational Leader Award and the President's Distinguished Administrative Staff Award from Humber College.
